<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            height: 297mm;
            width: 210mm;
            background: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20mm;
        }
        
        .cover-image {
            max-width: 80%;
            max-height: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 15mm;
        }
        
        .title {
            font-size: 36pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #3f51b5;
            margin-bottom: 8mm;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 160mm;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 15mm;
        }
        
        .author {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: auto;
        }
        
        .year {
            font-size: 12pt;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5mm;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img class="cover-image" src="docs/assets/cover.png" alt="Cover">
    
    <h1 class="title">The Serial Bioinformatician</h1>
    
    <p class="subtitle">
        A comprehensive guide from the central dogma to cutting-edge 
        computational techniques in bioinformatics.
    </p>
    
    <p class="author">Raymond Otoo, Ph.D.</p>
    <p class="year">2026</p>
</body>
</html>